  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Innovative Insurance Products for Climate Change Adaptation</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aimed to help Ghana manage the socio-economic costs and risks associated with climate change. It did so by developing and placing on the market climate-related agricultural insurance schemes for selected value chains. The project involved cooperation with regulatory and supervisory bodies, insurance companies and insurance industry associations, as well as consumers. In addition, a project knowledge management component on climate risk insurances in the IKI was added at a later stage.</narrative>
  </description>
